cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with automatic text summarization, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR), making cs.CL and cs.IR the most likely categories. The use of clustering and ontologies also suggests a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence (AI), making cs.AI a likely category as well. The visualization aspect of the paper may also fall under the scope of data visualization and graphics, making cs.SI a possible category. Finally, the use of X-means for clustering suggests a focus on unsupervised learning, making cs.LG a possible category as well.
